ckground_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-11263964 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"11263964\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Velikost na\u0161ega zaboja je: Dol\u017eina: 60, \u0160irina: 40, Vi\u0161ina: 44 cm. Da pa boste la\u017eje na\u010drtovali in najeli pravilno \u0161tevilo box-ov, si lahko pomagate z na\u0161imi splo\u0161nimi smernicami o \u0161tevilu \u0161katel, ki jih obi\u010dajno potrebujete za posamezen prostor \u2013 od garsonjere pa vse do 3 sobnega stanovanja.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4672f67a e-grid e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"4672f67a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5b4804a2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5b4804a2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Garsonjera:<\/strong><\/p><p>15-30 boxov<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-47636a9d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"47636a9d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>1 sobno stanovanje:<\/strong><\/p><p>30-40 boxov<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-36a9e63e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"36a9e63e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>2 sobno stanovanje:<\/strong><\/p><p>40-60 boxov<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f52a6b4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f52a6b4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>3 sobno stanovanje:<\/strong><\/p><p>60-80 boxov<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7867967b e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"7867967b\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-82141ca elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"82141ca\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Prednosti plasti\u010dnih zabojev za ve\u010dkratno uporabo<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b0e2f21 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"b0e2f21\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-68c4038f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"68c4038f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Zakaj bi se obremenjevali z nepotrebnimi kartonskimi \u0161katlami in lepilnim trakom, ko si lahko najamete selitveno \u0161katlo z vsem potrebnim materialom? Na\u0161i plasti\u010dni selitveni zaboji za najem so hitrej\u0161a in cenej\u0161a re\u0161itev, s katero bo va\u0161a naslednja selitev manj stresna in potratna.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-44d896b0 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"44d896b0\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fb9660c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"fb9660c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5><strong>Preprosto in zlo\u017eljivo <\/strong><strong>\u2713<\/strong><\/h5><p>Na\u0161i zaboji za selitev, ki jih lahko najamete, \u017ee imajo pokrov. Brez lepilnega traku ali sestavljanja \u0161katel in brez nereda pri recikliranju. Na\u0161i plasti\u010dni zaboji za selitev in za ve\u010dkratno uporabo so tudi trdni in mo\u010dni, da bodo va\u0161i predmeti med prevozom varni. Poleg tega jih je mogo\u010de zlagati!<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-42e16bec e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"42e16bec\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-55e7df16 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"55e7df16\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5><strong>Hitreje <\/strong><strong>\u2713<\/strong><\/h5><p>Hiter najem selitvenih zabojev Rabimbox. Preprosto izra\u010dunajte, koliko zabojev potrebujete, in dostavili vam jih bomo na dom. Ko jih imate, jih samo zapakirajte, zlo\u017eite in odpeljite.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9753821 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"9753821\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-63a03ed elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"63a03ed\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5><strong>Ceneje <\/strong><strong>\u2713<\/strong><\/h5><p>Pri najemu plasti\u010dnih selitvenih \u0161katel za ve\u010dkratno uporabo Rabimbox vam ni treba kupovati kartonskih \u0161katel in lepilnega traku, poleg tega pa tudi ne izgubite \u010dasa z sestavo!<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3dc5f4ab e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"3dc5f4ab\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-33ecde8f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"33ecde8f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6bce5dca elementor-widget elementor-widg